<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>FINAL SURVEY</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css"/>
</head>
<body style="margin: auto;">
  <header><% include ./header %></header>
  <div class="container-info" style="height:200px; width:700px;">
    <h2>Almost done!</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Finally, we have a few questions about you.</p>
    <br>
    <div class="container-feedback">
      <form action="/action_page.php">
        <label for="country">Please enter your country of residence</label>
        <input type="text" id="country" name="country" placeholder="Your country..">
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="sex">What is your gender?</label>
        <select id="sex" name="sex">
          <option value="select">Please select</option>
          <option value="male">Male</option>
          <option value="female">Female</option>
        </select>
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="birth">What is your year of birth?</label>
        <input type="number" min="1900" max="2018" step="1" placeholder="xxxx" />
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="region">Do you live in an urban, rural or suburban region?</label>
        <select id="region" name="country">
          <option value="select">Please select</option>
          <option value="urban">Urban</option>
          <option value="rural">Rural</option>
          <option value="suburban">Suburban</option>
        </select>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p>In order to consider you for the lottery which allow you to win a voucher, please indicate your contact details.</p>
        <p>In case you win, we will contact you via email.</p>
        <br>
        <label for="fname">First name</label>
        <input type="text" id="fname" name="firstname" placeholder="Your first name..">
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="lname">Last name</label>
        <input type="text" id="lname" name="lastname" placeholder="Your last name..">
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="email">E-mail address</label>
        <input type="text" id="mail" name="email_address" placeholder="Your email-address..">
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="final">At last, we want to ask you if there is anything that you would like to share with us?</label>
        <br>
        <textarea id="final" name="final" placeholder="Write something.." style="height:150px; width:500px;">
        </textarea>
      </form>
        </div>
      <br>
      <br>
        <div class ="text-muted">
        <p>
          Please press the "Complete" button to submit your information and to finish the fictious online purchase process.
        </p>
      </div>
    <button class="btn-complete" onclick="location.href ='http://localhost:8080/thankyou'">Complete</button>
</div>
  <br>
  <div class="progress-feedback">
  <div class="progress">
    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 100%"></div>
  </div>
</div>
  <footer>
    <% include ./footer %>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
